= Presentation

This presentation is written in Asciidoc and meant to be converted to HTML + reveal-js.

== Setup

The setup is based on the official instructions:
https://docs.asciidoctor.org/reveal.js-converter/latest/setup/standalone-executable/

Install the Asciidoc converter:

  $ sudo gem install asciidoctor-revealjs
  $ asciidoctor-revealjs --version
  Asciidoctor reveal.js 4.1.0 using Asciidoctor 2.0.17 [https://asciidoctor.org]
  Runtime Environment (ruby 3.0.4p208 (2022-04-12 revision 3fa771dded) [x86_64-linux]) (lc:UTF-8 fs:UTF-8 in:UTF-8 ex:UTF-8)

Install the javascript part:

  $ git clone -b 3.9.2 --depth 1 https://github.com/hakimel/reveal.js.git

== Presentation

To convert the Asciidoc source material to HTML:

  $ asciidoctor-revealjs --out-file=presentation.html presentation.adoc

